name: LookupPoint
tag_list: microsoft, microsoft-gold-certified-partner, microsoft-office, microsoft-word, microsoft-excel, microsoft-outlook, microsoft-sharepoint, sharepoint, power-users, it-administrators, microsoft-office-2010, line-of-business-systems, agresso, oracle, sunsyste
overview:
LookupPoint is a productivity tool that gives Microsoft Office users fast access to business information stored in multiple and disparate ERP and line-of-business systems, from within their Microsoft Office environment.

Users mouse over business items in any Outlook email, Word document or Excel spread sheet and LookupPoint will return the relevant business information aggregated in an information panel directly in Microsoft Office.

The solution was created by Spanish Point Technologies Ltd, a Dublin, Ireland based software consultancy. Spanish Point is a Microsoft Gold Certified Partner and Worldwide Partner of the Year Winners.
